Change  English name of Zosterops vellalavella from Belted White-eye to Vella Lavella White-eye (Dutson 2012)
Split widespread Cape White-eye from restricted Z.pallidus (Oatley 2011). Retain English name Cape White-eye (Hockey, Dean & Ryan eds 2005). Z. virens has page priority over Z. capensis
Zosterops wallacei is related to Lophozosterops complex (Moyle et al 2009).
Separate 5 species of Philippine Stachyris babblers to Zosterornis in the Zosteropidae (Moyle et al. 2009)
